# 🏗️ Technical Architecture – FitTrack

## Overview
FitTrack is built on the MERN stack with real-time updates and robust testing and deployment pipelines.

---

## 📂 Project Structure

### Backend
- Express server with Mongoose models
- RESTful API + JWT authentication
- Socket.io for real-time updates

### Frontend
- React + Tailwind
- Recharts for analytics
- Axios for API calls

---

## 🧪 Testing
- Jest & Supertest (API)
- React Testing Library (UI)
- Cypress (End-to-end)

---

## 🧵 CI/CD
- GitHub Actions
- Vercel & Render deployments
- Auto-build on push to `main`

---

## 🔍 Monitoring
- Sentry (error tracking)
- Logtail (logs)
